told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20interview%20with%2021-year-old%20creator%20and%20influencer%20Rhegan%20Coursey.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20small%20down%20near%20Dallas%2C%20Texas%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20pursuing%20social%20media%20for%20as%20long%20as%20I%20can%20remember.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20made%20my%20first%20videos%20in%20fourth%20grade%3A%20I%20taught%20myself%20how%20to%20edit%2C%20got%20a%20professional%20camera%2C%20and%20posted%20all%20sorts%20of%20content%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20I%20saw%20Los%20Angeles%20as%20the%20coolest%20place%20ever.%20I%20knew%20LA%20was%20the%20place%20where%20influencers%20lived%2C%20the%20place%20to%20be%20when%20you%20wanted%20to%20do%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20time%20in%20seventh%20grade%2C%20I%20told%20my%20dad%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20live%20in%20LA%20one%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20I%20%26quot%3Bblew%20up%26quot%3B%20on%20TikTok%20and%20gained%20an%20audience%2C%20moving%20to%20LA%20was%20at%20the%20top%20of%20my%20mind.%20A%20video%20of%20mine%20went%20viral%20in%20March%20of%202020%2C%20and%20after%20that%20it%20was%20boom%2C%20boom%2C%20boom%2C%20back%20to%20back.%20I%20gained%20a%20million%20followers%20really%20fast.%20I%20didn't%20even%20have%20time%20to%20process%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20of%202021%2C%20I%20visited%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20and%20in%20the%20span%20of%20three%20days%2C%20I%20found%20an%20apartment%20and%20signed%20a%20lease.%20I%20had%20recently%20turned%2018%2C%20and%20I%20went%20behind%20my%20parents'%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20texted%20my%20mom%20about%20my%20decision%20to%20move%20while%20I%20was%20on%20my%20flight%20back%20to%20Texas%2C%20and%20she%20wasn't%20happy.%20She%20felt%20betrayed.%20I%20spent%20one%20more%20month%20at%20home%2C%20and%20then%20moved%20into%20my%20apartment%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20horrible%20about%20it%20now%2C%20but%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20do%20whatever%20it%20took%20to%20be%20in%20LA.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20wasn't%20going%20to%20grow%20as%20a%20content%20creator%20if%20I%20wasn't%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELA%20is%20great%2C%20until%20it's%20not%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20very%20first%20night%20in%20LA%2C%20I%20got%20blackout%20drunk.%20I'm%20not%20mad%20at%20myself%20for%20that%2C%20it%20was%20my%20first%20night.%20But%20then%20I%20did%20it%20for%20three%20months%20straight.%20Every%20single%20night%2C%20I%20was%20drinking%2C%20going%20out.%20I%20lost%20all%20motivation%20for%20content%20creating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20hanging%20out%20with%20people%20I'd%20met%20on%20social%20media%2C%20we%20were%20going%20to%20parties%20in%20mansions.%20In%20LA%2C%20people%20use%20partying%20as%20a%20distraction%20from%20their%20responsibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20usually%20aren't%20normal%20parties%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20a%20list%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20bring%20your%20ID%20to%20match%20the%20name%20on%20the%20list%2C%20and%20those%20who%20are%20not%20on%20the%20list%20will%20sometimes%20just%20jump%20fences%20and%20sneak%20in.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20in%20LA%20want%20to%20live%20the%20celebrity%20life%2C%20without%20actually%20being%20celebrities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20months%20after%20moving%20to%20the%20city%2C%20I%20got%20contacted%20by%20a%20content%20house%20called%20%26quot%3BGo%20House.%26quot%3B%20I%20would%20live%20in%20a%20mansion%20and%20create%20content%20with%20other%20influencers%20who%20were%20staying%20there.%20I%20ended%20up%20living%20in%20the%20house%20for%20six%20months%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20happened%20during%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20met%20my%20first%20boyfriend%2C%20my%20first%20love.%20I%20was%20not%20treated%20well%2C%20and%20within%20that%2C%20I%20met%20people%20that%20pretended%20to%20be%20my%20friends%20just%20to%20get%20close%20to%20my%20boyfriend.%20I%20had%20friends%20who%20hooked%20up%20with%20him%20behind%20my%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20I%20started%20to%20realize%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20around%20a%20bunch%20of%20people%20that%20are%20treating%20each%20other%20like%20their%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Girl%20with%20long%20black%20hair%20waring%20a%20crochet%20white%20top%20and%20skirt%2C%20standing%20in%20a%20field%20with%20a%20ferris%20wheel%20in%20the%20background%20at%20sunset.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65280f5068f1d46f52b0150a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECoursey%20attending%20Coachella%20in%20April%202023%2C%20a%20few%20days%20before%20starting%20the%20fitness%20challenge%20that%20coincided%20with%20a%20wider%20lifestyle%20change.%20%3Cp%3ERhegan%20Coursey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20want%20to%20move%20back%20to%20Texas%2C%20to%20be%20with%20my%20family%20and%20live%20a%20normal%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20LA%2C%20everyone%20wants%20to%20be%20someone%2C%20and%20they're%20willing%20to%20go%20great%20lengths%20to%20get%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20struggling%20financially%20because%20it%20is%20so%20expensive.%20They%20want%20to%20live%20this%20celebrity%20lifestyle%20so%20they%20can%20post%20on%20social%20media%20that%20they%20spent%20%2420%20on%20a%20smoothie%20at%20luxury%20grocery%20store%20Erewhon.%20You're%20pretending%20to%20be%20someone%20that's%20not%20you%2C%20and%20then%20you%20lose%20yourself.%20That's%20the%20cycle%20of%20LA.%20That's%20what%20I%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20became%20so%20disconnected%20from%20my%20family%2C%20I%20did%20not%20visit%20home%20for%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20finally%20decided%20to%20go%20back%2C%20it%20was%20because%20my%20little%20cousin%20had%20committed%20suicide%20at%20the%20age%20of%2012.%20The%20night%20before%20I%20was%20meant%20to%20fly%2C%20someone%20broke%20into%20my%20car%20and%20stole%20my%20documents%2C%20as%20well%20as%20%242%2C000%20worth%20of%20clothing%20I%20had%20just%20sold%20on%20a%20second-hand%20website.%20That%20was%20the%20third%20time%20I%20had%20gotten%20robbed%20in%20three%20months.%20I%20missed%20my%20flight%20the%20next%20day%20because%20I%20was%20at%20the%20police%20station%20trying%20to%20sort%20my%20passport%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20snowballed%20into%20a%20feeling%20of%20unease.%20Los%20Angeles%20feels%20dark.%20It%20never%20feels%20homey.%20As%20a%2021-year-old%20woman%20living%20by%20herself%2C%20I%20rarely%20feel%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%20this%20year%2C%20I%20impulsively%20started%20a%20fitness%20challenge%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0waking%20up%20early%2C%20reading%20self-help%20books%2C%20doing%20two%20workouts%20a%20day%2C%20eating%20healthy.%20It%20kickstarted%20this%20cycle%20of%20wanting%20to%20become%20the%20best%20version%20of%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20documented%20it%20on%20social%20media%2C%20and%20gained%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20followers.%20It%20opened%20up%20the%20doors%20for%20me%20of%20making%20lifestyle%20content%20that%20pushes%20other%20people.%20It's%20not%20just%20for%20me%20anymore%2C%20it's%20a%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20I%20connect%20with%20my%20followers%20and%20work%20on%20myself%2C%20the%20more%20I'm%20realizing%20that%20there's%20so%20much%20more%20to%20life%20than%20getting%20blackout%20drunk%20until%204%20a.m.%2C%20going%20home%20and%20sleeping%20in%20until%205%20p.m.%2C%20and%20doing%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20miss%20my%20family%2C%20I%20miss%20being%20at%20home.%20I%20also%20think%20that%20my%20content%20would%20do%20better%20in%20Dallas%20because%20I'd%20be%20living%20a%20more%20normal%20life.%20I'm%20not%20a%20celebrity.%20Yes%2C%20I%20get%20to%20experience%20bits%20and%20pieces%20of%20that%20life%2C%20but%20at%20my%20core%2C%20I'm%20a%20normal%20person%20that%20likes%20normal%20things%2C%20and%20I%20d