%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0Yonatan%20Kedem%20Siman%20Tov%2C%20his%20wife%20Tamar%20Kedem-Siman%20Tov%2C%20and%20their%20three%20young%20children%20-%206-year-old%20twin%20girls%20Shahar%20and%20Arbel%20and%204-year-old%20son%20Omer%2C%20as%20well%20as%20his%2070-year-old%20mother%20Carol%20Siman%20Tov%20were%20all%20killed%20at%20Nir%20Oz%20kibbutz%20outside%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20family%C2%A0fled%20to%20a%20safe%20room%20when%20Hamas%20rockets%20began%20landing.%20They%20texted%20friends%20and%20relatives%20they%20were%20safe%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fterrorists-murdered-entire-young-family-sheltering-in-kibbutz-nir-oz-saferoom%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Times%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0Tamar%2C%20wrote%20to%20her%20friends%20on%20WhatsApp%20saying%2C%20''Hi%20guys%2C%20we%20got%20into%20the%20shelter%20in%20our%20house%2C%20we're%20all%20going%20okay.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20an%20hour%20later%2C%20the%20Hamas%20operatives%20entered%20the%20safe%20room%20and%20fired%20at%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E''They're%20here.%20They're%20burning%20us.%20We're%20suffocating%2C''%20Yonatan%20Kedem%20Siman%20Tov%20texted%20his%20sister%20Ranae%20Butler%20moments%20before%20being%20killed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20messages%20soon%20stopped.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFamily%20friend%2C%20Yishai%20Lacob%2C%20posted%20on%20Facebook%3A%20''Our%20hearts%20are%20shattered.%20An%20entire%20family%20was%20killed%20by%20evil%20murderers%20who%20shot%20the%20children%20and%20parents%20simply%20because%20they%20were%20Jewish.%20And%20this%20is%20just%20one%20story%2C%20among%20so%20many.%20It's%20unbearable.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Yonatan%20Siman%20Tov%20was%20a%20wheat%20farmer%2C%20Tamar%20Kedem-Siman%20Tov%20was%20a%20community%20leader%20running%20to%20become%20head%20of%20the%20Eshkol%20Regional%20Council.%C2%A0She%20also%20served%20as%20an%20advisor%