esports%20events%20around%20the%20world%20expand%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20John%20Robinson%2C%20president%20of%20US%20esport%20organization%20100%20Thieves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20inclusion%20of%20esports%20alongside%20more%20traditional%20events%20like%20athletics%20and%20cycling%20has%20prompted%20some%20discussion%20over%20whether%20it%20should%20qualify%20as%20a%20sport%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurther%20controversy%20was%20sparked%20by%20the%20news%20that%20the%20South%20Korean%20medallists%20would%20temporarily%20exempt%20them%20from%20compulsory%20military%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korea%20grants%20exemptions%20to%20athletes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20classical%20and%20traditional%20musicians%20and%20some%20dancers%2C%20who%20win%20top%20prizes%20in%20their%20respective%20fields%2C%20The%20Associated%20Press%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223947%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22South%20Korea's%20Kim%20Gwanwoo%20(L)%20poses%20with%20his%20gold%20medal%20during%20an%20award%20ceremony%20after%20winning%20the%20%26quot%3BStreet%20Fighter%20V%3A%20Champion%20Edition%26quot%3B%20final%20esports%20event%20during%20the%202022%20Asian%20Games%20in%20Hangzhou%20in%20China's%20eastern%20Zhejiang%20province%20on%20September%2028%2C%202023.%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651e829e6561dd877e7100bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222631%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESouth%20Korea's%20Kim%20Gwanwoo%20won%20gold%20for%20Street%20Fighter%20V%3A%20Champion%20Edition.%20%3Cp%3EWANG%20ZHAO%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEsports%20are%20also%20on%20the%20International%20Olympic%20Committee's%20radar.%20In%20June%20the%20IOC%20held%20an%20esports%20event%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Folympics.com%2Fioc%2Fesports-faq%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estating%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20supported%20%26quot%3Bthe%20growth%20of%20virtual%20sports%20within%20the%20Olympic%20movement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Olympic%20Esports%20Series%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20global%20virtual%20and%20simulated%20sports%20competition%20created%20by%20the%20IOC%2C%20and%20in%20collaboration%20with%20International%20Federations%20and%20game%20publishers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20event%20included%2010%20games%20such%20as%20sailing%2C%20archery%2C%20and%20cycling%20instead%20of%20fan%20favorites%20such%20as%20LoL%2C%20and%20was%20criticized%20for%20failing%20to%20reflect%20the%20true%20landscape%20of%20competitive%20esports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatt%20Woods%2C%20CEO%20of%20esports%20marketing%20and%20talent%20agency%20AFK%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fgames%2F2023%2Fmar%2F08%2Fpushing-buttons-olympic-games-esports-competition%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20questioned%20the%20IOC's%20decisions.%20%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20working%20with%20existing%20game%20publishers%20or%20well-established%20tournaments%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20the%20Olympic%20committee%20has%20instead%20decided%20to%20use%20this%20event%20as%20a%20marketing%20vehicle%20for%20brand-new%2C%20poorly%20thought%20out%2C%20unlicensed%20mobile%20games.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20another%20complicating%20factor%20about%20including%20esports%20in%20competitions%20such%20as%20the%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrant%20Rousseau%20of%20gaming%20organization%20Team%20Falcons%20told%20Insider%3A%20%26quot%3BSomeone%20owns%20each%20and%20every%20sport%20in%20esports%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20very%20large%20difference%20compared%20to%20traditional%20sports.%20To%20bring%20all%20these%20different%20publishers%20together%20is%20extremely%20difficult.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHanding%20over%20competitive%20control%20to%20a%20group%20under%20a%20'traditional%20sport'%20design%20who%2C%20to%20be%20frank%2C%20don't%20understand%20esports%20to%20the%20depth%20they%20do%2C%20certainly%20isn't%20