-123101500501_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fmcap-of-six-of-top-10-firms-jumps-rs-70-527-11-crore-ril-biggest-gainer-123101500501_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Wire%20Protests%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20LG%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Separatist%20Ecosystem%E2%80%99%20Charge%20Against%20Correspondent%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F15160522%2FF28AVhZaUAARAph.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20written%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20lieutenant%20governor%20(LG)%20Manoj%20Sinha%20objecting%20to%20his%20accusation%20that%20its%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20correspondent%20Jehangir%20Ali%20is%20part%20of%20some%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Cseparatist%20ecosystem%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAli%20had%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanoj-sinha-jammu-kashmir-bajaj-allianze-pmjay%5C%22%3EIAS%20officer%20Ashok%20Kumar%20Parmar%E2%80%99s%20allegations%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20under%20Sinha%20rejected%20the%20advice%20of%20the%20finance%20and%20law%20departments%20on%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri-Jan%20Arogya%20Yojna%20insurance%20scheme%20to%20amend%20a%20multi-crore%20contract%20midway%20to%20favour%20a%20private%20insurance%20company.%20He%20also%20filed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjammu-kashmir-ias-officer-pmjay-manoj-sinha%5C%22%3Efollow-up%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20said%20that%20despite%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%E2%80%99s%20denial%20of%20the%20IAS%20officer%E2%80%99s%20claims%2C%20several%20questions%20about%20the%20insurance%20scheme%20remain.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20public%20event%20in%20Jammu%20on%20October%2014%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailyexcelsior.com%2Fanti-india-separatist-corrupt-