ur%20and%20a%20half%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20so%20naive%20and%20thought%20we%20were%20going%20to%20sell%20our%20house%20in%20San%20Antonio%20and%20it%20would%20be%20so%20easy%20to%20find%20a%20house%20in%20Austin.%20We%20ended%20up%20staying%20at%20Scott's%20aunt's%20house%20for%20four%20and%20a%20half%20months%2C%20which%20I%20don't%20recommend%20any%20family%20with%20a%20newborn%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBuying%20a%20house%20in%20Austin%20was%20so%20much%20harder%20than%20we%20expected%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20just%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20to%20expect%20in%20the%20housing%20market.%20It%20was%20really%20hard%20and%20really%20daunting%2C%20and%20very%20defeating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20being%20in%20our%20young%20thirties%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20we%20were%20relatively%20successful.%20We%20had%20been%20really%20smart%20with%20our%20finances.%20It%20was%20a%20hard%20pill%20to%20swallow%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BMan%2C%20how%20did%20we%20not%20get%20that%20house%3F%26quot%3B%20We%20were%20just%20up%20against%20people%20that%20were%20completely%20out%20of%20our%20league.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20made%20multiple%20offers%20on%20multiple%20houses%20and%20we%20were%20constantly%20outbid.%20We%20were%20going%20up%20against%20people%20making%20cash%20offers%20from%20out%20of%20state%2C%20sight-unseen.%20Trying%20to%20find%20a%20house%20in%20the%20neighborhoods%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20live%20in%20was%20extremely%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20is%20be%20in%20a%20house%20and%20create%20a%20home%20with%20my%20family%2C%20and%20it%20took%20so%20much%20longer%20than%20I%20was%20expecting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222095%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20baby%20sitting%20on%20the%20front%20lawn%20of%20a%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65298bb268f1d46f52b17fde%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHollingsworth's%20second%20daughter%2C%20Zoey%2C%20in%20front%20of%20their%20home%20in%20Austin.%3Cp%3ESarah%20Hollingsworth%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20decided%20to%20expand%20the%20perimeter%20in%20which%20we%20were%20willing%20to%20live.%20We%20found%20ourselves%20buying%20a%20house%20in%20West%20Austin%2C%20in%20the%20neighborhood%20Bee%20Cave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20closed%20in%20March%202020%2C%20and%20truly%2C%20I%20think%20it%20was%20the%20universe's%20way%20of%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20this%20is%20the%20right%20place%20at%20the%20right%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20because%20then%20the%20world%20shut%20down.%20But%20we%20had%20a%20neighborhood%20community%20with%20sidewalks%20and%20parks%20and%20we%20were%20thankfully%20in%20our%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20so%20fortunate%20that%20we%20bought%20our%20house%20when%20we%20did%20because%20if%20we%20tried%20to%20find%20this%20house%20today%2C%20we%20would%20be%20completely%20out-priced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20three%20bedrooms%2C%20two%20baths%2C%20with%20a%20two-car%20garage%2C%20and%20a%20pretty%20small%20backyard%2C%20but%20it's%20the%20perfect%20size%20for%20my%20now%20two%20kids.%20It%20cost%20around%20%24400%2C000%20and%20is%20about%201%2C700%20square%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20bought%20our%20house%20in%20San%20Antonio%20for%20much%20less.%20It%20was%20%24325%2C000%20and%20was%20similar%20in%20size.%20We%20basically%20just%20moved%20to%20a%20more%20expensive%20city%20for%20pretty%20much%20the%20same%20house%20that%20would%20cost%20a%20little%20bit%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20felt%20like%20I%20hit%20the%20jackpot%20when%20I%20moved%20to%20Austin%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20motivation%20for%20moving%20to%20Austin%20at%20the%20time%20was%20my%20husband%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20career%20change.%20We%20were%20both%20working%20at%20a%20tech%20company%20headquartered%20in%20San%20Antonio.%20There%20really%20just%20aren't%20that%20many%20high-paying%20tech%20jobs%20in%20San%20Antonio%20and%20we%20both%20loved%20that%20industry%20and%20wanted%20to%20stay%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAustin%2C%20being%20the%20next-closest%20tech%20city%2C%20had%20an%20abundant%20amount%20of%20high-paying%20tech%20jobs.%20My%20husband%20was%20recruited%20and%20ultimately%20ended%20up%20working%20at%20a%20tech%20company%20in%20Austin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20was%20in%20tech%20when%20I%20moved%20here%20in%202019%2C%20but%20I%20actually%20resigned%20from%20my%20position%20in%20January%20of%202020%2C%20because%20I%20had%20this%20idea%20for%20my%20startup%2C%20Poppylist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20enrolled%20in%20the%20Entrepreneur%20Center%20of%20Austin%2C%20which%20San%20Antonio%20doesn't%20have.%20Capital%20Factory%2C%20a%20co-working%20space%20in%20Austin%2C%20always%20had%20tech%20and%20coffee%20chats%20that%20I%20would%20attend.%20I%20was%20completely%20immersed%20in%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20never%20afraid%20to%20go%20to%20places%20where%20I%20might%20meet%20people%20that%20I%20could%20learn%20something%20from%20or%20who%20could%20potentially%20be%20helpful.%20I%20went%20to%20Techstars%20Austin%20demo%20day%2C%20sitting%20in%20the%20audience%20and%20listening%20to%20people%20pitch%20their%20ideas%20and%20meeting%20the%20Techstar%20staff.%20There%20were%20just%20so%20many%20opportunities%20in%20Austin%20for%20someone%20with%20no%20entrepreneur%20experience%20to%20get%20fully%20immersed%20and%20start%20learning%20and%20meeting%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20I%20would've%20started%20Poppylist%20no%20matter%20where%20I%20was%20located%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20I%20would've%20been%20able%20to%20accelerate%20that%20business%20idea%20and%20get%20it%20off%20the%20ground%20as%20quickly.%20I%20think%20Austin%20and%20the%20people%20I%20met%20and%20got%20to%20know%20really%20helped%20move%20things%20forward%2C%20and%20I%20got%20to%20connect%20with%20people%20pretty%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20like%20I%20hit%20the%20jackpot%20when%20I%20moved%20to%20Austin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20proximity%20to%20outdoor%20activities%20is%20unbeatable%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20biggest%20thing%20that%20we%20realized%20after%20living%20in%20Austin%20is%20just%20how%20much%20we%20love%20walking%20and%20being%20outside.%20Austin%20is%20not%20a%20walkable%20city%20by%20any%20means%2C%20but%20we%20have%20miles%20and%20miles%20of%20sidewalks%20in%20our%20neighborhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that%20we%20were%20so%20grateful%20for%20was%20access%20to%20outdoor%20activities.%20We%20have%20access%20to%20Greenbelt%20trails%20in%20our%20neighborhood%2C%20and%20Lake%20Austin.%20They%20just%20built%20this%20beautiful%20trail%20from%20the%20beginning%20of%20our%20neighborhood%20all%20the%20way%20down%20to%20the%20water%20through%20the%20country.%20We%20can%20walk%20down%20our%20neighborhood%20and%20go%20jump%20in%20Lake%20Austin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20selfie%20of%20a%20husband%20and%20wife%20and%20their%20two%20daughters.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65298a8555f52b01b35f5bfe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHollingsworth%2C%20her%20husband%2C%20Scott%2C%20and%20their%20two%20children%2C%20Amelia%20and%20Zoey.%3Cp%3ESarah%20Hollingsworth%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESan%20Antonio%20is%20getting%20better%20on%20outdoor%20activities%2C%20it's%20not%20really%20an%20active%20city.%20There's%20not%20a%20ton%20to%20do%20outside%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20anything%20like%20Austin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20the%20energy%20this%20city%20has.%20I%20love%20the%20way%20the%20city%20feels%20in%20the%20fall%20and%20in%20the%20winter%20when%20people%20are%20outside%20and%20the%20music%20festival%20scene%20starts%20happening%2C%20like%20Austin%20City%20Limits.%20It's%20like%20everyone's%20been%20hibernating%20and%20trying%20to%20survive%20the%20grueling%20summer%2C%20and%20then%20it's%20like%20everyone%20reemerges%20and%20there's%20thi