-sachin-tendulkars-bilkooool-thanda-post-4482704%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shoaib%20Akhtar%20responded%20to%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20after%20being%20trolled%20over%20Pakistan's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20loss%20against%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Four-friendly-banter-doesnt-shoaib-akhtar-responds-to-sachin-tendulkars-bilkooool-thanda-post-4482704%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Four-friendly-banter-doesnt-shoaib-akhtar-responds-to-sachin-tendulkars-bilkooool-thanda-post-4482704%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Four-friendly-banter-doesnt-shoaib-akhtar-responds-to-sachin-tendulkars-bilkooool-thanda-post-4482704%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vaccine%20hesitancy%20is%20a%20problem%20for%20dogs%20too%2C%20study%20finds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225367%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Veterinary%20technicians%20vaccinate%20a%20dog%20outside%20the%20vehicle%20at%20a%20drive-through%20pet%20vaccine%20clinic%20at%20Mission%20Viejo%20Animal%20Services%20Center%20amid%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20on%20June%2023%2C%202020%20in%20Mission%20Viejo%2C%20California.%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652a9e258bed706e837cb769%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223585%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20dog%20is%20vaccinated%20at%20a%20drive-through%20clinic%20in%20California%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3Cp%3EMario%20Tama%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHesitancy%20among%20dog%20owners%20means%20some%20pets%20are%20not%20being%20vaccinated%2C%20new%20research%20found.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20study%20in%20the%20journal%20Vaccine%20highlighted%20the%20risks%20to%20both%20animal%20and%20human%20populations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EResearchers%20say%20misinformation%20on%20social%20media%20and%20rising%20veterinary%20bills%20are%20behind%20the%20problem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20surprisingly%20high%20number%20of%20dog%20owners%20are%20concerned%20about%20getting%20their%20animals%20vaccinated%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS0264410X23010150%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20the%20scientific%20journal%20Vaccine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20survey%20of%202%2C200%20adults%20conducted%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%2037%25%20of%20dog%20owners%20said%20they%20viewed%20vaccines%20for%20their%20pets%20as%20unsafe%2C%20while%2030%25%20regarded%20them%20as%20unnecessary%20and%2022%25%20said%20they%20were%20ineffective.%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EA%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eslight%20majority%3Cspan%3E%20of%20dog%20owners%20(53%25)%20endorse%20at%20least%20one%20of%20these%20three%20positions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20researchers%20noted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20concluded%20that%20the%20increased%20skepticism%20around%20pet%20vaccinations%20was%20being%20driven%20my%20misinformation%20on%20social%20media%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20rising%20cost%20of%20veterinary%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%2C%20titled%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3ESick%20as%20a%20dog%3F%20The%20prevalence%2C%20politicization%2C%20and%20health%20policy%20consequences%20of%20canine%20vaccine%20hesitancy%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%20found%20cross-over%20in%20disproved%20theories%20relating%20to%20human%20vaccination.%20For%20example%2C%2040%25%20of%20respondents%20believed%20that%20vaccines%20could%20cause%20autism%20in%20their%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20declining%20numbers%20of%20vaccinated%20pets%20don't%20just%20endanger%20animal%20populations%20but%20risk%20the%20spread%20of%20vaccine-preventable%20diseases%20to%20humans%20as%20well%2C%20per%20the%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Motta%20of%20Boston%20University's%20School%20of%20Public%20Health%20and%20a%20lead%20researcher%20on%20the%20study%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fhealth%2Fveterinarians-anti-vax-movement-pets-600fa7bb%3Fmod%3Dhp_lead_pos11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20and%20his%20colleagues%20were%20shocked%20by%20their%20findings.%20%26quot%3BIn%20a%20world%20where%20mandates%20are%20being%20dialed%20back%20and%20more%20pets%20go%20unvaccinated%2C%20that's%20a%20threat%20to%20our%20pets%20but%20also%20a%20public%20health%20threat%20to%20you%20and%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2050%20million%20households%20in%20the%20US%20own%20a%20dog%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.avma.org%2Fresources-tools%2Freports-statistics%2Fus-pet-ownership-statistics%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Veterinary%20Medical%20Association.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20to%20stop%20the%20spread%20of%20a%20disease%20like%20rabies%2C%20which%20humans%20typically%20contract%20from%20an%20animal%20bite%2C%20more%20than%2070%25%20of%20the%20dog%20population%20must%20have%20been%20vaccinated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20majority%20of%20US%20states%20require%20rabies%20vaccinations%2C%20but%20it%20is%20the%20only%20vaccine%20to%20be%20widely%20mandated.%20While%20animal%20diseases%20are%20well%20contained%2C%20the%20researchers%20warned%20that%20infectious%20diseases%20could%20spread%20if%20the%20trend%20revealed%20in%20their%20study%20persisted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F8-coronavirus-vaccine-myths-debunked-from-microchipping-to-mandates-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espread%20of%20misinformation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20vocal%20protests%20against%20vaccine%20mandates%2C%2081.4%25%20of%20the%20US%20population%20has%20now%20had%20at%20least%20one%20dose%20of%20a%20COVID-19%20vaccine%2C%20and%2069.5%25%20have%20completed%20a%20primary%20series%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcovid.cdc.gov%2Fcovid-data-tracker%2F%23vaccinations_vacc-people-booster-percent-pop5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECDC%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdog-owners-vaccine-hesitancy-problem-research-journal-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697364679000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652aa07c55f52b01b35fc37d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdog-owners-vaccine-hesitancy-problem-research-journal-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20dog%20owners%20are%20concerned%20about%20the%20risks%20of%20getting%20their%20animals%20vaccinated%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20study%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20Vaccine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pthompson%40insider.com%20(Polly%20Thompson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdog-owners-vaccine-hesitancy-problem-research-journal-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Speciality%20Restaurants%20to%20focus%20on%20oriental%20cuisine%20for%20expansion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697364640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F15%2Ffull%2F1697364175-0807.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fspeciality-restaurants-to-focus-on-oriental-cuisine-for-expansion-123101500463_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cloud%20kitchens%2C%20which%20expanded%20quickly%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20will%20continue%20to%20grow%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fspeciality-restaurants-to-