r%20informing%20the%20IT%20department%20on%20September%2028%20of%20his%20difficulties%2C%20they%20promptly%20discovered%20that%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20access%20his%20membership%20site%20since%20the%20information%20in%20the%20system%2C%20especially%20his%20email%20address%2C%20did%20not%20belong%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BOn%20the%205th%20Day%20of%20August%202022%2C%20Brian%20Mwenda%20Ntwiga%20was%20admitted%20to%20the%20Bar%20and%20his%20correct%20email%20address%20was%20captured%20and%20an%20Account%20opened%20for%20him%20in%20the%20Advocates%20portal.%20We%20reached%20out%20to%20Advocate%20Brian%20Mwenda%20Ntwiga%20who%20confirmed%20that%20he%20had%20not%20applied%20for%20a%20practicing%20certificate%20since%20his%20admission%2C%20reason%20being%20that%20he%20had%20been%20working%20at%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20Attorney%20General%20and%20did%20not%20require%20a%20Practicing%20Certificate%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Law%20Society%20of%20Kenya%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20only%20until%20sometime%20in%20September%202023%20when%20he%20attempted%20to%20login%20into%20the%20system%20and%20activate%20his%20profile%20to%20apply%20for%20his%20Practising%20Certificate%20that%20he%20realised%20he%20could%20not%20access%20his%20LSK%20Portal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20revealed%20that%20after%20being%20granted%20access%20to%20the%20platform%2C%20Brian%20Mwenda%20modified%20his%20profile%20photo%2C%20applied%20for%2C%20and%20paid%20for%20his%20practising%20certificate.%20%26quot%3BUpon%20being%20allowed%20access%20to%20the%20account%2C%20he%20took%20control%20of%20the%20portal%20and%20changed%20his%20profile%20picture%2C%20the%20workplace%20and%20applied%20and%20paid%20for%20the%20practicing%20certificate.%20However%2C%20his%20application%20was%20not%20processed%20since%20he%20was%20required%20to%20provide%20documents%20including%20the%20certificate%20of%20business%20incorporation%2C%26quot%3B%