m%20feeds%20on%20such%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20doubt%20and%20confusion%20about%20the%20constitution.%20Hence%20the%20proliferation%20of%20decrees%20and%20ordinances%2C%20and%20bills%20being%20passed%20hurriedly%20by%20voice%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20long%20existence%20under%20such%20circumstances%20makes%20the%20people%20docile%20and%20ready%20to%20follow%20the%20new%20rules%20of%20the%20game%20unquestioningly.%20In%202023%2C%20we%20learn%20countries%20earlier%20considered%20%E2%80%98friends%E2%80%99%20must%20now%20be%20seen%20as%20unfriendly%20under%20the%20new%20treaties%20signed%20by%20those%20who%20live%20and%20work%20only%20in%20the%20vast%20time%20not%20available%20to%20us.%20The%20more%20space%20the%20Vast%20Time%20buys%20for%20the%20state%2C%20the%20less%20there%20is%20for%20us%20to%20ponder%20over%20the%20new%20developments.%20We%20accept%20projects%20and%20new%20buildings%20made%20with%20public%20money%20being%20gifted%20personally%20to%20us%20by%20the%20leadership.%20We%20accept%20becoming%20stooges%20to%20superpowers%20we%20see%20shaking%20hands%20and%20giving%20bear%20hugs%20to%20our%20leadership.%20The%20future%20shall%2C%20we%20learn%2C%20no%20longer%20grow%20organically%20out%20of%20our%20known%20historical%20past%20but%20a%20new%20world%20order%2C%20newer%20coalitions%20that%20mandate%20a%20new%20interpretation%20of%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESchools%2C%20colleges%2C%20and%20institutions%20all%20must%20abandon%20old%20history%20and%20subscribe%20to%20new%20ones%20even%20if%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20make%20sense.%20Our%20subjective%20time%20seems%20to%20have%20ceased%20to%20matter.%20Suddenly%20a%20war%20erupts%20far%20off%20but%20our%20media%20is%20feeding%20us%20a%20mish-mash%20of%20irrational%20images%2C%20myths%2C%20make-believe%2C%20illusory%20visuals%3A%20leaders%20launching%20billion%20rupee%20projects%2C%20new%20trains%2C%20new%20colleges%2C%20speaking%20to%20students%20of%20a%20new%20AI-armed%20tech-savvy%20India%2C%20flying%20off%20suddenly%20and%20seen%20next%20in%20the%20remotest%20idyllic%20setting%20praying%20to%20ancient%20gods%20with%20Vedic%20rituals.%20Kishore%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20lines%20spoken%20to%20a%20dictatorial%20mother%20come%20to%20mind%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EAapne%20iss%20ghar%20ko%20Swarga%20aur%20hum%20subko%20Swargvaasee%20bnaa%20diya%20hai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(You%20have%20made%20this%20home%20into%20heaven%20and%20we%20are%20now%20all%20heaven%20dwellers)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnly%20the%20irrational%2C%20you%20find%20endures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20pattern%20followed%20is%20the%20same%20all%20the%20world%20over.%20First%2C%20they%20come%20for%20those%20who%20create%20values%20to%20destroy%20those%20who%20know%20what%20those%20values%20are.%20Then%20you%20co-opt%20value%20givers%E2%80%99%20phrases%20from%20the%20abandoned%20past%20and%20use%20them%20to%20great%20effect%20in%20international%20gatherings%20of%20like-minded%20new%20friends.%20Then%20you%20hand%20the%20baton%20to%20the%20media%20and%20they%20fill%20the%20space%20with%20loud%20music%20from%20a%20totally%20make-believe%20band.%20By%20now%20one%20can%20recognise%20the%20bespoke%20spokespersons%20of%20this%20brave%20new%20world%3A%20the%20ever-furious%20moustachioed%20generals%20and%20%E2%80%9Cdomain%20experts%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20constantly%20interjecting%20anchors%20with%20their%20mile-long%20questions%20answered%20with%20more%20questions%20by%20shrieking%20spokespersons%2C%20the%20matronly%20motormouths%20with%20their%20perfectly%20lacquered%20nails%20and%20pouting%20red%20O%20mouths.%20The%20only%20unforgivable%20crime%20is%20an%20open%20confrontation%20with%20the%20real%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20media%E2%80%99s%20salvation%20is%20trying%20to%20achieve%20what%20it%20can%20no%20longer%20achieve%2C%20the%20trust%20of%20consumers.%20Most%20of%20us%20the%20world%20over%2C%20frankly%20read%20the%20papers%20and%20watch%20the%20news%20like%20%3Cstrong%3Es%3C%2Fstrong%3Etale%20jokes%20written%20by%20some