%20breaking%20and%20inundating%20vast%20swathes%20of%20land%20and%20killing%20hundreds%2C%20of%20earthquakes%2C%20tsunamis%2C%20and%20cyclones%20killing%20and%20destroying%20thousands%20of%20homes%20just%20brings%20on%20no%20protest%20marches%20or%20public%20effort%20to%20bail%20out%20the%20affected.%20Those%20in%20proximity%20keep%20making%20videos%20of%20mountains%20crumbling%2C%20homes%20disappearing%20in%20gorges%2C%20and%20bombs%20reducing%20whole%20human%20clusters%20to%20ash%20and%20dust.%20Among%20those%20who%20are%20watching%20it%20on%20their%20laptops%20or%20smartphones%2C%20it%20only%20brings%20a%20sad%20shrug%20and%20rolling%20of%20eyes%2C%20%E2%80%9CAh%2C%20the%20Climate%20Change!%E2%80%99%20The%20war%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20or%20Armenia%20or%20Ukraine%20is%20similarly%20dismissed%20as%20a%20natural%20mutation%20of%20%E2%80%9Chistoric%20cycles%20of%20ethnic%20warfare%E2%80%9D.%20And%20the%20media%20pushes%20its%20agenda%20further%20by%20colouring%20it%20with%20religious%20tones%20so%20strong%20that%20human%20misery%20gets%20hidden.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20wonder%20loneliness%2C%20depression%20and%20drug%20addiction%20are%20on%20an%20unprecedented%20rise%20everywhere.%20You%20feel%20you%20cannot%20stop%20this%20juggernaut%2C%20you%20just%20throw%20yourself%20under%20its%20wheels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20would%20it%20mean%20if%20one%20saw%20war%20as%20it%20really%20is%3F%20It%20means%20to%20see%20human%20nature%20in%20its%20greatest%20pitch%20of%20tension%2C%20terror%2C%20and%20cruelty.%20But%20if%20the%20media%20will%2C%20as%20it%20does%20each%20day%2C%20reduce%20the%20whole%20tragedy%20to%20black%20and%20white%2C%20the%20Good%20on%20the%20one%20side%20and%20the%20Baddies%20on%20the%20other%2C%20war%20seems%20like%20a%20video%20game%20played%20indoors%20with%20little%20breaks%20for%20food%20and%20a%20quick%20smoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20time%20our%20media%20cut%20across%20the%20linguistic%20walls%20of%20China%20to%20accept%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20great%20divide%20within%20it.%20Also%20how%20war%20magnifies%20everything%20associated%20with%20everything%20from%20history%20to%20language%3A%20emotion%2C%20fury%2C%20wild%20exultation%2C%20stubbornness%2C%20and%20xenophobia.%20They%20give%20you%20a%20high%20before%20they%20destroy%20professions%20and%20professionals.%20Real-time%20wars%20on%20the%20ground%20or%20during%20elections%20are%20waged%20mostly%20through%20information%20dissemination%20in%20local%20language%20media.%20It%20is%20one-sided%20mostly%20and%20will%20answer%20no%20nuanced%20questions%2C%20only%20old%20answers%20neatly%20copied%20and%20cut-pasted%20from%20religious%20texts%20and%20military%20leaders%E2%80%99%20biographies%20in%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20our%20media%20today%20is%20in%20possession%20of%20tools%20for%20accurate%20information%20and%20verification%20from%20so%20many%20sources%20and%20in%20so%20many%20languages.%20It%20must%20re-establish%20the%20fast-evaporating%20relationship%20between%20ideas%20and%20structures%20among%20the%20common%20men%20and%20women.%20The%20struggle%20for%20the%20future%20of%20the%20earth%20is%20taking%20place%20more%20and%20more%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20people%E2%80%99s%20language%20where%20propaganda%20wars%20are%20waged%20using%20vernaculars%20as%20an%20effective%20tool%20of%20action.%20Without%20realising%2C%20most%20war%20reporters%20seem%20to%20see%20things%20on%20the%20war%20front%20as%20the%20authorities%20wish%20them%20to%20see.%20To%20be%20independent%20as%20a%20war%20reporter%20is%20not%20necessarily%20to%20criticise%20them%20but%20to%20step%20out%20of%20false%20theories%20of%20historic%20rights%20and%20wrongs%20and%20begin%20to%20see%20and%20report%20human%20beings%20as%20fellow%20human%20beings%20rooted%20in%20one%E2%80%99s%20personal%20space%20and%20personal%20reflections%2C%20capable%20of%20%E2%80%98feeling%E2%80%99%20the%20pain%20they%20describe.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697353501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%