s%20ready%2C%20we%20take%20the%20cost%20to%20the%20customer%20and%20then%20finalise%20the%20deal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%20comes%20the%20step%20of%20fabrication.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20factories%2C%20the%20steel%20frames%20are%20fabricated%20using%20advanced%20machinery.%20The%20sections%20are%20brought%20to%20the%20place%20and%20assembled%20there.%20If%20you%20look%20from%20outside%2C%20it%20would%20resemble%20a%20steel%20structure%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-8-1697118217.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20structure%20is%20quite%20lightweight%20so%20it%20does%20not%20need%20any%20machinery%20to%20do%20the%20fitting.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-8-1697118217.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-8-1697118217-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-8-1697118217-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-8-1697118217-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-8-1697118217-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332118%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20structure%20is%20quite%20lightweight%20so%20it%20does%20not%20need%20any%20machinery%20to%20do%20the%20fitting.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20ODF%20Group%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20structures%20are%20very%20lightweight%20so%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20any%20machines%20to%20do%20the%20fittings.%20Hence%2C%20they%20can%20be%20done%20ea