0he%20released%20after%20taking%20charge%20of%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EDTNext%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Palanivel%20said%20that%20Veeramuthuvel%20is%20the%20first%20graduate%20in%20their%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20Veeramuthuvel%E2%80%99s%20time%20pursuing%20a%20diploma%20in%20mechanical%20engineering%20at%20a%20polytechnic%20college%20that%20he%20discovered%20his%20first%20passion.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20pursuing%20the%20diploma%2C%20I%20got%20interested%20in%20engineering.%20I%20secured%2090%20percent%20marks%20in%20all%20papers%20and%20got%20an%20engineering%20seat%20on%20merit%20in%20the%20Shri%20Sai%20Ram%20Engineering%20College%20in%20Chennai%20for%20a%20Bachelor%20of%20Engineering%20course%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETransforming%20from%20an%20average%20student%2C%20he%20began%20excelling%20in%20engineering.%20From%20then%20on%2C%20he%20consistently%20ranked%20first%20or%20second%20in%20every%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20was%20not%20that%20I%20was%20studying%20all%20the%20time.%20But%20when%20I%20was%20engaged%20with%20my%20studies%2C%20I%20would%20try%20to%20study%20with%20100%20percent%20focus%20and%20make%20an%20effort%20to%20understand%20everything%20that%20I%20studied.%20This%20is%20the%20reason%20I%20was%20able%20to%20secure%20good%20marks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20secured%20admission%20to%20the%20then%20REC%2C%20which%20is%20today%20called%20NIT%20Trichy%2C%20for%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20engineering%2C%20in%20which%20he%20also%20excelled%20with%20a%209.17%20CGPA.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Hard%20work%20will%20never%20go%20unrewarded%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%20Mission%3A%3Cbr%3E%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3Vikram%20soft-landed%20on%20%F0%9F%8C%96%2C%20again!%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EVikram%20Lander%20exceeded%20its%20mission%20objectives.%20It%20successfully%20underwent%20a%20hop%20experiment.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EOn%20command%2C%20it%20fired%20the%20engines%2C%20elevated%20itself%20by%20about%2040%20cm%20as%20expected%20and%20landed%20safely%20at%20a%20distance%20of%2030%20%E2%80%93%2040%20cm%20away.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FT63t3MVUvI%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FT63t3MVUvI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1698570774385205621%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%204%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EVeeramuthuvel%E2%80%99s%20career%20began%20at%20Lakshmi%20Machine%20Works%20in%20Coimbatore%2C%20where%20he%20developed%20a%20deep%20interest%20in%20aerospace%20engineering.%20Subsequently%2C%20he%20worked%20in%20the%20research%20and%20development%20division%20of%20the%20helicopter%20division%20of%20Hindustan%20Aeronautics%20Limited%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331067%2Framji-swaminathan-craftizan-miniature-models-of-isro-rockets-satellites-chandrayaan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edesign%20engineer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHaving%20dreamt%20of%20working%20in%20ISRO%20since%20his%20college%20days%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20ISRO%20Satellite%20Centre%20as%20a%20project%20engineer%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20he%20worked%20on%20multiple%20remote%20sensing%20and%20scientific%20satellites%2C%20and%20with%20the%20Mars%20Orbiter%20Mission%20in%202013.%20He%20also%20enrolled%20in%20a%20PhD%20at%20IIT%20Madras%20to%20fuel%20his%20love%20for%20research%20after%20joining%20ISRO.%20His%20doctorate%20is%20on%20the%20topic%20%E2%80%98Vibration%20Suppression%20of%20Electronic%20Package%20in%20Satellites%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVeeramuthuvel%20led%20ISRO%E2%80%99s%20inaugural%20nanosatellite%20t