%20trees%20and%20vegetables%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Anirudh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnirudh%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20was%20more%20than%20happy%20to%20take%20it%20on.%20Designing%20a%20farm%20stay%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20a%20forest%20is%20not%20a%20project%20one%20comes%20across%20every%20day.%20As%20he%20describes%20the%20features%20of%20the%20farm%20stay%20spread%20across%20the%20four-acre%20land%2C%20one%20can%20tell%20how%20seamlessly%20the%20raw%20finesse%20of%20the%20property%20blends%20into%20the%20surrounding%20foliage.%20A%20process%20that%20lasted%20over%20two%20years%20saw%20the%20light%20of%20day%20six%20months%20ago%20when%20Anirudh%20handed%20the%20keys%20over%20to%20the%20trio.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20design%20philosophy%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20looking%20for%20a%20typical%20South%20Indian%20traditional%20home%20with%20a%20courtyard%20that%20would%20wrap%20itself%20around%20the%20front%20of%20the%20house.%20The%20courtyard%20would%20be%20a%20communal%20sit-out%20area%20where%20they%20could%20relax%20in%20the%20evenings%20and%20enjoy%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327701%2Fcouple-restores-woodway-estate-british-era-home-into-heritage-homestay-in-chikmagalur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglorious%20view%20of%20the%20farmland%3C%2Fa%3E%20overlooking%20the%20valley.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20friends%20insisted%20on%20an%20open-plan%20system%20with%20as%20few%20walls%20as%20possible.%20So%2C%20Anirudh%20shares%20that%20while%20the%20bedrooms%20and%20toilets%20are%20enclosed%2C%20the%20living%20room%2C%20dining%20room%20and%20kitchen%20spaces%20are%20continuous.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20property%20has%20been%20built%20keeping%20mud%20as%20the%20hero%20element%2C%20with%20stone%20filling%20in%20the%20spaces.%20What%20this%20does%20aside%20from%20being%20an%20aesthetic%20addition%20i